{"id":622727,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/11/香港01｜网传林夕作品内地全数下架-内地网民：《/","date":"2019-11-23T05:24:52Z","modified":"2019-11-23T05:24:52Z","title":"香港01｜网传林夕作品内地全数下架 内地网民：《北京欢迎你》呢？","content":"<p>自反修例风波越演越烈，不少网络流通的讯息亦开始难分其真确性，就如昨日（22/11）音乐圈中疯传一则微博讯息，表示林夕将被内地全面封杀，包括下架所有林夕作品及禁止提及此人。其实林夕作为香港第一词人，在政治上的取态相当明显，亦不时在自己的专栏中发表立场及想法，故此成为封杀对象也并不意外。</p>\n<p>而两岸三地的乐迷听到这消息，反应却出奇地一致，甚至一向「仇黄」的内地网民也有部份支持林夕的声音。有人认为内地若封杀林夕，便是广东歌没落的开端，毕竟林夕出道至今，填词作品多达近4000首，有内地网民表示：「那太多歌都不能听了吧，粤语区重灾不可想像。」更有网民笑言：「连内地歌手也不能再唱《北京欢迎你》？」</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/aEOPMGaVWmS1_PFBLP9Qc3_H83VYmDYBAqoaiAKqGog.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-622732\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/aEOPMGaVWmS1_PFBLP9Qc3_H83VYmDYBAqoaiAKqGog.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"663\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/aEOPMGaVWmS1_PFBLP9Qc3_H83VYmDYBAqoaiAKqGog.jpeg 540w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/aEOPMGaVWmS1_PFBLP9Qc3_H83VYmDYBAqoaiAKqGog-204x300.jpeg 204w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/1hCA2v9z407i5M7Ekss-3rFykwvfYWzKsYVj_rGFY_4.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-622731\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/1hCA2v9z407i5M7Ekss-3rFykwvfYWzKsYVj_rGFY_4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/1hCA2v9z407i5M7Ekss-3rFykwvfYWzKsYVj_rGFY_4.jpeg 540w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/1hCA2v9z407i5M7Ekss-3rFykwvfYWzKsYVj_rGFY_4-169x300.jpeg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/NeKO2nVXKETNB7H0DkOTv0Qm36-pYMFrWeupzlnrqc4.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-622733\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/NeKO2nVXKETNB7H0DkOTv0Qm36-pYMFrWeupzlnrqc4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/NeKO2nVXKETNB7H0DkOTv0Qm36-pYMFrWeupzlnrqc4.jpeg 540w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/NeKO2nVXKETNB7H0DkOTv0Qm36-pYMFrWeupzlnrqc4-169x300.jpeg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/NQda6I3a_QRYtvszlxMgvC4GFPjtyunH9DlA7fQ5QO0.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-622734\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/NQda6I3a_QRYtvszlxMgvC4GFPjtyunH9DlA7fQ5QO0.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/NQda6I3a_QRYtvszlxMgvC4GFPjtyunH9DlA7fQ5QO0.jpeg 540w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/NQda6I3a_QRYtvszlxMgvC4GFPjtyunH9DlA7fQ5QO0-169x300.jpeg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>内地网民亦意见不一，引起激烈讨论</p></blockquote>\n<p>诚然，若林夕被封杀，的确会把不少人处于尴尬境地，就如正在内地进行巡回演出的杨千嬅，全盛时期的作品几乎也是出自林夕之手，而林夕对杨千嬅也份外偏爱，你能想像到杨千嬅内地巡演中没有《少女的祈祷》、《再见二丁目》、《飞女正传》、《小城大事》等作品吗？</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_622735\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/P7nx2BmcLQ5wNUAA37LsiSMI2qFnoBHwniFgP54hYD8.jpeg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-622735\" class=\"wp-image-622735\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/P7nx2BmcLQ5wNUAA37LsiSMI2qFnoBHwniFgP54hYD8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/P7nx2BmcLQ5wNUAA37LsiSMI2qFnoBHwniFgP54hYD8.jpeg 1920w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/P7nx2BmcLQ5wNUAA37LsiSMI2qFnoBHwniFgP54hYD8-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/P7nx2BmcLQ5wNUAA37LsiSMI2qFnoBHwniFgP54hYD8-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/P7nx2BmcLQ5wNUAA37LsiSMI2qFnoBHwniFgP54hYD8-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/P7nx2BmcLQ5wNUAA37LsiSMI2qFnoBHwniFgP54hYD8-1536x1152.jpeg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/P7nx2BmcLQ5wNUAA37LsiSMI2qFnoBHwniFgP54hYD8-1080x810.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-622735\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">正于内地进行巡回演出，如果杨千嬅不能唱林夕的作品，演唱会歌单还剩下多少歌？</p></div>\n<p>不过网传消息毕竟未经核实，记者在内地指标性音乐平台「网易云音乐」、「虾米音乐」等搜寻过，发现绝大部分的林夕作品仍然存在，林夕的名字也未被屏蔽，不过部份歌曲如陈奕迅的《六月飞霜》则未能搜寻。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-622727 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/11/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af01%ef%bd%9c%e7%bd%91%e4%bc%a0%e6%9e%97%e5%a4%95%e4%bd%9c%e5%93%81%e5%86%85%e5%9c%b0%e5%85%a8%e6%95%b0%e4%b8%8b%e6%9e%b6-%e5%86%85%e5%9c%b0%e7%bd%91%e6%b0%91%ef%bc%9a%e3%80%8a/2s2mj5edg5_l4-ohoa3if7q5npi3zrhwofwk4kbccua/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2S2Mj5eDg5_L4-OHOA3If7q5npI3zrhWoFwK4KBcCuA-150x150.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2S2Mj5eDg5_L4-OHOA3If7q5npI3zrhWoFwK4KBcCuA-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2S2Mj5eDg5_L4-OHOA3If7q5npI3zrhWoFwK4KBcCuA-440x440.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/11/2S2Mj5eDg5_L4-OHOA3If7q5npI3zrhWoFwK4KBcCuA-50x50.jpeg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item